<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8"/>
  <meta content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" name="viewport"/>
  <title>Polyglot - Apprenez facilement de nouvelles langues</title>
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet"/>
  <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet"/>
  <style>
    :root {
      --primary-color: #3f51b5;
      --secondary-color: #ff4081;
      --spanish-color: #F1BF00;
      --french-color: #318CE7;
      --english-color: #CF142B;
      --portuguese-color: #006600;
    }
    
    body {
      font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;
      background-color: #f5f5f5;
      min-height: 100vh;
    }
    
    .navbar-brand {
      font-size: 1.8rem;
      font-weight: 700;
    }
    
    .hero-section {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 5rem 0;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f5f7fa 0%, #c3cfe2 100%);
    }
    
    .hero-heading {
      font-size: 3.5rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      background: linear-gradient(45deg, var(--primary-color), var(--secondary-color));
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      background-clip: text;
      color: transparent;
      display: inline-block;
    }
    
    .language-grid {
      margin-top: 4rem;
    }
    
    .language-card {
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
      border-radius: 15px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
      margin-bottom: 30px;
      border: none;
      height: 100%;
    }
    
    .language-card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-10px);
      box-shadow: 0 15px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
    }
    
    .card-spanish {
      border-top: 5px solid var(--spanish-color);
    }
    
    .card-french {
      border-top: 5px solid var(--french-color);
    }
    
    .card-english {
      border-top: 5px solid var(--english-color);
    }
    
    .card-portuguese {
      border-top: 5px solid var(--portuguese-color);
    }
    
    .language-icon {
      font-size: 3rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }
    
    .card-spanish .language-icon {
      color: var(--spanish-color);
    }
    
    .card-french .language-icon {
      color: var(--french-color);
    }
    
    .card-english .language-icon {
      color: var(--english-color);
    }
    
    .card-portuguese .language-icon {
      color: var(--portuguese-color);
    }
    
    .language-title {
      font-size: 1.8rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }
    
    .features-section {
      padding: 5rem 0;
      background-color: white;
    }
    
    .feature-icon {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      color: var(--primary-color);
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }
    
    .feature-title {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }
    
    .footer {
      background-color: #343a40;
      color: white;
      padding: 3rem 0;
    }
    
    .footer a {
      color: #adb5bd;
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: color 0.2s;
    }
    
    .footer a:hover {
      color: white;
    }
    
    .footer-title {
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }
    
    .social-icon {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      margin-right: 1rem;
    }
    
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .hero-heading {
        font-size: 2.5rem;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
<!-- Navbar -->
<nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-dark bg-primary">
  <div class="container">
    <a class="navbar-brand" href="/">
      <i class="fas fa-language me-2"></i>Polyglot
    </a>
    <button aria-controls="navbarNav" aria-expanded="false" aria-label="Toggle navigation" class="navbar-toggler" data-bs-target="#navbarNav" data-bs-toggle="collapse" type="button">
      <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
    </button>
    <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navbarNav">
      <ul class="navbar-nav ms-auto">
        <li class="nav-item">
          <a class="nav-link active" href="#">Accueil</a>
        </li>
        <li class="nav-item">
          <a class="nav-link" href="#features">Fonctionnalités</a>
        </li>
        <li class="nav-item">
          <a class="nav-link" href="#about">À propos</a>
        </li>
        <li class="nav-item">
          <a class="nav-link" href="#contact">Contact</a>
        </li>

        <% if (locals.session && locals.session.user) { %>
          <li class="nav-item">
            <a class="nav-link" href="/dashboard">Dashboard</a>
          </li>
          <li class="nav-item">
            <a class="nav-link text-danger" href="/logout">Déconnexion</a>
          </li>
        <% } %>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</nav>

<!-- Hero Section -->
<section class="hero-section">
  <div class="container">
    <h1 class="hero-heading">Apprenez une nouvelle langue facilement</h1>
    <p class="lead mb-4">Choisissez parmi nos 4 langues et commencez votre voyage linguistique dès aujourd'hui</p>
    <div class="row language-grid">
      <!-- Espagnol -->
      <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-3">
        <div class="card language-card card-spanish">
          <div class="card-body text-center p-4">
            <div class="language-icon">
              <i class="fas fa-sun"></i>
            </div>
            <h3 class="language-title">Espagnol</h3>
            <p class="text-muted mb-3">¡Hola! Aprende español de forma divertida</p>
            <a class="btn btn-outline-primary w-100 mb-2" href="/espagnol">Commencer</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <!-- Français -->
      <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-3">
        <div class="card language-card card-french">
          <div class="card-body text-center p-4">
            <div class="language-icon">
              <i class="fas fa-utensils"></i>
            </div>
            <h3 class="language-title">Français</h3>
            <p class="text-muted mb-3">Bonjour ! Apprends le français facilement</p>
            <a class="btn btn-outline-primary w-100 mb-2" href="/francais">Commencer</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <!-- Anglais -->
      <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-3">
        <div class="card language-card card-english">
          <div class="card-body text-center p-4">
            <div class="language-icon">
              <i class="fas fa-globe-americas"></i>
            </div>
            <h3 class="language-title">Anglais</h3>
            <p class="text-muted mb-3">Hello! Learn English in a fun way</p>
            <a class="btn btn-outline-primary w-100 mb-2" href="/anglais">Commencer</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <!-- Portugais -->
      <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-3">
        <div class="card language-card card-portuguese">
          <div class="card-body text-center p-4">
            <div class="language-icon">
              <i class="fas fa-guitar"></i>
            </div>
            <h3 class="language-title">Portugais</h3>
            <p class="text-muted mb-3">Olá! Aprenda português facilmente</p>
            <a class="btn btn-outline-primary w-100 mb-2" href="/portugais">Commencer</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="py-5 bg-light">
  <div class="container text-center">
    <h2 class="mb-5">Explorez nos modules complémentaires</h2>
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
        <div class="card h-100 shadow-sm border-0">
          <div class="card-body">
            <i class="fas fa-cross fa-3x text-primary mb-3"></i>
            <h5 class="card-title">Christ</h5>
            <p class="card-text">Approfondissez votre foi avec des enseignements bibliques, prières et méditations.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
        <div class="card h-100 shadow-sm border-0">
          <div class="card-body">
            <i class="fas fa-book fa-3x text-success mb-3"></i>
            <h5 class="card-title">Culture Générale</h5>
            <p class="card-text">Enrichissez vos connaissances à travers des quiz, anecdotes et faits historiques.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
        <div class="card h-100 shadow-sm border-0">
          <div class="card-body">
            <i class="fas fa-utensils fa-3x text-danger mb-3"></i>
            <h5 class="card-title">Recettes de Cuisine</h5>
            <p class="card-text">Découvrez des recettes savoureuses du monde entier pour tous les niveaux.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Features Section -->
<section class="features-section" id="features">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="text-center mb-5">Pourquoi choisir notre méthode d'apprentissage ?</h2>
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-4 text-center mb-4">
        <div class="feature-icon">
          <i class="fas fa-comments"></i>
        </div>
        <h3 class="feature-title">Dialogues immersifs</h3>
        <p>Apprenez à travers des dialogues authentiques générés par IA, qui simulent des conversations réelles.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-4 text-center mb-4">
        <div class="feature-icon">
          <i class="fas fa-clone"></i>
        </div>
        <h3 class="feature-title">Flash Cards intelligentes</h3>
        <p>Mémorisez le vocabulaire efficacement grâce à notre système de flash cards adaptatif.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-4 text-center mb-4">
        <div class="feature-icon">
          <i class="fas fa-headphones"></i>
        </div>
        <h3 class="feature-title">Prononciation authentique</h3>
        <p>Écoutez et pratiquez avec des voix natives pour améliorer votre prononciation.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row mt-4">
      <div class="col-md-4 text-center mb-4">
        <div class="feature-icon">
          <i class="fas fa-book-open"></i>
        </div>
        <h3 class="feature-title">Histoires captivantes</h3>
        <p>Plongez dans des histoires interactives qui renforcent vos compétences linguistiques.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-4 text-center mb-4">
        <div class="feature-icon">
          <i class="fas fa-graduation-cap"></i>
        </div>
        <h3 class="feature-title">Exercices pratiques</h3>
        <p>Renforcez vos acquis avec des exercices variés adaptés à votre niveau.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-4 text-center mb-4">
        <div class="feature-icon">
          <i class="fas fa-mobile-alt"></i>
        </div>
        <h3 class="feature-title">Accessible partout</h3>
        <p>Apprenez où que vous soyez, sur tous vos appareils, même hors ligne.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Footer -->
<footer class="footer" id="contact">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
        <h4 class="footer-title">À propos de Polyglot</h4>
        <p>Polyglot est une plateforme d'apprentissage de langues innovante qui utilise l'intelligence artificielle pour créer des expériences d'apprentissage personnalisées.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
        <h4 class="footer-title">Liens rapides</h4>
        <ul class="list-unstyled">
          <li><a href="#">Accueil</a></li>
          <li><a href="#features">Fonctionnalités</a></li>
          <li><a href="#about">À propos</a></li>
          <li><a href="#contact">Contact</a></li>
          <li><a href="#">Confidentialité</a></li>
          <li><a href="#">Conditions d'utilisation</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
        <h4 class="footer-title">Contactez-nous</h4>
        <p><i class="fas fa-envelope me-2"></i> info@polyglot-learn.com</p>
        <p><i class="fas fa-phone me-2"></i> +33 1 23 45 67 89</p>
        <div class="mt-4">
          <a class="social-icon" href="#"><i class="fab fa-facebook"></i></a>
          <a class="social-icon" href="#"><i class="fab fa-twitter"></i></a>
          <a class="social-icon" href="#"><i class="fab fa-instagram"></i></a>
          <a class="social-icon" href="#"><i class="fab fa-youtube"></i></a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row mt-4">
      <div class="col-12 text-center">
        <p class="mb-0">© <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Polyglot. Tous droits réservés.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>

<!-- Bootstrap JS -->
<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
<script>
  // Animation smooth scroll pour les liens d'ancrage
  document.querySelectorAll('a[href^="#"]').forEach(anchor => {
    anchor.addEventListener('click', function (e) {
      e.preventDefault();
      
      document.querySelector(this.getAttribute('href')).scrollIntoView({
        behavior: 'smooth'
      });
    });
  });
</script>
</body>
</html>